<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 04:08:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊朗爆炸造成近100人死亡加剧中东紧张局势</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-blasts-qassem-soleimani-israel-hamas-war/articleshow/106530926.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106530926.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗表示，伊朗中部发生的造成近100人死亡的袭击是为了惩罚其对以色列的立场。伊朗指挥官卡西姆·苏莱马尼坟墓附近的袭击造成 95 人死亡、211 人受伤。伊朗称其反对以色列是墓地袭击的动机。美国国务院发言人马特·米勒表示，“我们没有理由相信以色列参与了这次爆炸。”美国最初的假设是伊斯兰国或相关组织对此负责。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 03:42:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-blasts-qassem-soleimani-israel-hamas-war/articleshow/106530926.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本强烈地震造成 77 人死亡，救援人员在第四天争分夺秒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/rescuers-race-against-time-in-japan-on-day-4-after-powerful-earthquakes-leave-77-dead/articleshow/106530811.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106530811.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一场强烈地震后，救援人员沿着日本西海岸线搜寻幸存者，余震和海啸警报加剧了挑战。由于天气预报员警告可能出现大雨和山体滑坡，死亡人数上升至 77 人，仍有 35 人失踪。灾害专家强调需要进行准确的损失评估和适当的应对措施。专家表示，最初的 72 小时对于救援来说尤其关键，因为此后生存的可能性会大大降低。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 03:33:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/rescuers-race-against-time-in-japan-on-day-4-after-powerful-earthquakes-leave-77-dead/articleshow/106530811.cms</guid></item><item><title>恶作剧炸弹威胁迫使美国一些州议会大厦疏散</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hoax-bomb-threats-force-evacuations-of-some-us-statehouses/articleshow/106530347.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106530347.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一系列炸弹威胁迫使美国各州议会大厦疏散，但在警方没有发现爆炸物或可疑设备后，这些威胁被宣布为恶作剧。这些威胁针对康涅狄格州、佐治亚州、肯塔基州、密歇根州、密西西比州和蒙大拿州的州议会大厦。联邦调查局严肃对待恶作剧威胁，以保护无辜人民。密西西比州公共安全部和蒙大拿州行政总务部证实这些威胁并不可信。康涅狄格州州议会大厦在安全得到保证且警方清理州议会大厦后，在收到恶作剧威胁后重新开放。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 03:17:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hoax-bomb-threats-force-evacuations-of-some-us-statehouses/articleshow/106530347.cms</guid></item><item><title>到目前为止，关于伊朗致命爆炸的已知情况</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/whats-known-so-far-about-the-deadly-explosions-in-iran/articleshow/106529954.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106529954.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗克尔曼发生两起爆炸事件，造成至少 95 人死亡、210 多人受伤。此次袭击发生在卡西姆·苏莱马尼将军被杀四周年纪念活动期间。他的墓地附近发生的爆炸袭击了平民和紧急救援人员。没有任何组织声称对这起造成大规模人员伤亡的爆炸事件负责，这是自 1979 年伊斯兰革命以来伊朗最严重的袭击事件。此前伊朗发生的定点清除和破坏袭击并未涉及如此大规模的爆炸事件。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 03:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/whats-known-so-far-about-the-deadly-explosions-in-iran/articleshow/106529954.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国在朝鲜边境附近进行为期一周的射击演习</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/south-korea-us-conduct-week-long-firing-drills-near-north-korea-border/articleshow/106529461.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106529461.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;韩国和美国军队在朝鲜边境附近进行联合实战射击演习，导致朝鲜半岛紧张局势升级。此次演习旨在检验和增强抵御敌人侵略的战备能力。朝鲜批评这些演习是鲁莽的战争演习，并誓言要增加其核武库。联合演练涉及坦克、火炮、攻击机等110余件大型作战武器。此外，韩国海军还在多个地点进行了实弹演习和反潜演习。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:58:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/south-korea-us-conduct-week-long-firing-drills-near-north-korea-border/articleshow/106529461.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国警告胡塞武装停止袭击红海船只，否则将面临潜在的军事行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-warns-houthis-to-cease-attacks-on-red-sea-vessels-or-face-potential-military-action/articleshow/106529198.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106529198.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国及其盟国向胡塞武装发出最后警告，要求其停止攻击红海船只，否则将面临潜在的军事行动。胡塞武装针对以色列与哈马斯的战争发动了至少 23 次袭击。美国呼吁联合国安理会对胡塞武装采取行动，并警告其金融家伊朗不要支持叛乱分子。这些袭击针对的是通过关键的曼德海峡的商业船只。该公司表示，它将捍卫自己、利益、合作伙伴和国际商业。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:50:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-warns-houthis-to-cease-attacks-on-red-sea-vessels-or-face-potential-military-action/articleshow/106529198.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗指责以色列和美国在革命卫队将军苏莱马尼坟墓附近发生致命爆炸</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-blames-israel-us-for-deadly-blasts-near-grave-of-guards-general-soleimani/articleshow/106528968.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106528968.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗指责以色列和美国在该国南部发生两起爆炸事件，造成至少 95 人死亡。爆炸发生在革命卫队将军卡西姆·苏莱马尼的纪念活动期间，他在四年前的美国空袭中丧生。这些袭击被称为“恐怖袭击”，引发了人们对该地区冲突扩大的担忧。伊朗最高领导人指责“邪恶和犯罪的敌人”，并发誓要做出严厉回应。美国和以色列否认与爆炸事件有任何牵连。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:44:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-blames-israel-us-for-deadly-blasts-near-grave-of-guards-general-soleimani/articleshow/106528968.cms</guid></item><item><title>军方希望启动巴基斯坦的绿色革命</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/farming-revolution-pakistan-army-wants-to-overhaul-outdated-agriculture-sector/articleshow/106528687.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106528687.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦看到了乔利斯坦沙漠的农业潜力。政府计划租赁国有土地来改革农业部门。军方将在该项目中拥有大量股份，这引发了人们对公共土地利润的担忧。军队的参与可能会阻碍农业现代化所需的长期结构性改进。绿色巴基斯坦倡议旨在提高农作物产量并吸引外国投资。军队的参与可以为投资者提供稳定，但也有可能激怒农民。该倡议还旨在解决极端天气的后果并提高水的可持续性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/farming-revolution-pakistan-army-wants-to-overhaul-outdated-agriculture-sector/articleshow/106528687.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国伊玛目在新泽西清真寺外遭枪击身亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-imam-shot-outside-new-jersey-mosque-dies/articleshow/106528202.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106528202.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一位州检察官表示，周三在纽约附近一座清真寺外被枪杀的一名伊玛目已经死亡，他补充说，这起杀戮最初似乎并不是由“偏见”或国内恐怖主义造成的。检察官表示，这名男子哈桑·谢里夫在被送往医院之前身中多枪，随后不治身亡。新泽西州总检察长马特·普拉特金表示：“我们尚不清楚这起犯罪的动机，但迄今为止收集的证据并不表明这是出于偏见或国内恐怖主义的行为。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 01:42:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-imam-shot-outside-new-jersey-mosque-dies/articleshow/106528202.cms</guid></item><item><title>“克林顿可能出现在与爱泼斯坦有关的人名单中”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/clinton-could-be-in-list-of-people-tied-to-epstein/articleshow/106527926.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106527926.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 01:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/clinton-could-be-in-list-of-people-tied-to-epstein/articleshow/106527926.cms</guid></item><item><title>真主党主席：如果以色列选择与黎巴嫩开战，就没有上限或规则</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/no-ceilings-or-rules-if-israel-chooses-war-with-lebanon-hezbollah-chief/articleshow/106527821.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106527821.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 00:48:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/no-ceilings-or-rules-if-israel-chooses-war-with-lebanon-hezbollah-chief/articleshow/106527821.cms</guid></item><item><title>继《小熊维尼》之后，随着版权的终止，早期的米老鼠版本在恐怖电影中出演</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/after-pooh-early-mickey-mouse-version-stars-in-horror-film-as-copyright-ends/articleshow/106527929.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106527929.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 01:01:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/after-pooh-early-mickey-mouse-version-stars-in-horror-film-as-copyright-ends/articleshow/106527929.cms</guid></item><item><title>机组人员如何从火球喷气机中完成 18 分钟的奇迹救援</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/how-crew-pulled-off-18-minute-miracle-rescue-from-fireball-jet/articleshow/106527824.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106527824.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周二，日本航空一架客机在东京跑道上与一架小型飞机相撞，12 名机组人员花了 18 分钟才将 367 名乘客全部带下飞机并安全下落。日本第二大航空公司的官员根据机组人员的描述重建现场，表示机组人员按照教科书的方式遵循紧急程序，从第一条规则开始：恐慌控制。空客A350宽体客机一停下来，乘务员就呼吁乘客保持冷静。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 00:49:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/how-crew-pulled-off-18-minute-miracle-rescue-from-fireball-jet/articleshow/106527824.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本女子在火车上刺伤4人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/woman-stabs-4-on-train-in-japan/articleshow/106527843.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106527843.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 00:50:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/woman-stabs-4-on-train-in-japan/articleshow/106527843.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质12月在营救失败中死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-hostage-died-in-december-during-failed-rescue-bid/articleshow/106527822.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106527822.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 00:48:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-hostage-died-in-december-during-failed-rescue-bid/articleshow/106527822.cms</guid></item><item><title>真主党誓言对哈马斯杀戮作出回应，以色列处于高度戒备状态</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-on-high-alert-as-hezbollah-vows-response-for-hamas-killing/articleshow/106527768.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106527768.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列摩萨德情报部门负责人周三誓言，该机构将追捕所有参与 10 月 7 日以色列袭击事件的哈马斯成员，无论他们身在何处。在巴勒斯坦激进组织副头目在贝鲁特疑似以色列袭击中丧生的第二天，他做出了这一承诺。以色列拒绝对其实施杀戮的报道发表评论，但大卫·巴尼亚的评论似乎是最强烈的迹象，表明以色列是这起爆炸的幕后黑手。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 00:40:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-on-high-alert-as-hezbollah-vows-response-for-hamas-killing/articleshow/106527768.cms</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装称“瞄准”了红海的另一艘集装箱船</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/houthis-say-targeted-another-container-ship-in-the-red-sea/articleshow/106527772.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106527772.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 00:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/houthis-say-targeted-another-container-ship-in-the-red-sea/articleshow/106527772.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国担心暗杀可能影响谈判</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-worries-assassination-may-hit-talks/articleshow/106527771.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106527771.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 00:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-worries-assassination-may-hit-talks/articleshow/106527771.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国警方首次调查虚拟宇宙中女孩“阿凡达”的虚拟轮奸案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/in-a-first-uk-police-investigating-virtual-gang-rape-of-girls-avatar-in-metaverse/articleshow/106524371.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106524371.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据《纽约邮报》报道，英国警方正在调查涉嫌在虚拟现实游戏中轮奸一名女孩的案件，这似乎是此类案件中的第一起。据《纽约邮报》援引《每日邮报》报道，据称受害者是一名 16 岁以下的女孩，她在一款沉浸式游戏中戴着虚拟现实 (VR) 耳机，而她的化身（她的动画形象）被几名男子强奸。 。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 18:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/in-a-first-uk-police-investigating-virtual-gang-rape-of-girls-avatar-in-metaverse/articleshow/106524371.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列摩萨德主席誓言追捕哈马斯成员</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-mossad-chief-vows-to-hunt-down-hamas-members-a-day-after-senior-figure-killed-in-strike/articleshow/106524072.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106524072.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 17:30:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-mossad-chief-vows-to-hunt-down-hamas-members-a-day-after-senior-figure-killed-in-strike/articleshow/106524072.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>